dct_description_sm: Includes streeet index . Verso: 2 distance charts, 2 road sign charts, and illustrations. Shows foot print of indexed buildings and locations of gas stations, parks, banks, hotels, schools, churches, embassies, government buildings, hospitals, places of interest, and monuments.
dct_creator_sm: Instituto Geográfico Militar (Bolivia). Departamento de Geografía y Recursos Naturales, issuing body
dct_publisher_sm: La Paz : Instituto Geográfico Militar. Departmento de Geografía y Recursos Naturales, [1987].
